---
const splashres = await fetch("https://api.manczak.net/splash");
let splash = await splashres.text();
---
<section class="max-w-[48ch]">
  <h1 class="font-bold text-3xl font-lexend">jakub mańczak</h1>
  <p id="splash" class="text-neutral-500 pb-4 font-lexend cursor-pointer select-none">
    {splash || "splash not found :("}
  </p>
  <p>
    My name is Jakub Mańczak, people online call me jamesen
    and I'm learning IT in Poznań, Poland.
  </p>
</section>

